snippet.title: Cargo-Bot
snippet.description:
Cargo-Bot is the first game programmed entirely in Codea on iPad. It is available for free on the App Store. 

Cargo-Bot Link: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/cargo-bot/id519690804?ls=1&mt=8

Codea Link: http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/codea/id439571171?ls=1&mt=8

Music is "The Cannery" by Kevin MacLeod.
